Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Six, seven, eight, nine,\Nten, eleven, twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.35,0:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not that many.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.35,0:00:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you supposed\Nto read 12 books in one weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia\Nobviously thinks I can
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,or she would never have assigned\Nthem to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not planning\Non letting her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope you're not planning\Non sleeping, then, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Spike, why don't you\Ntake the day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really?\N- Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,These books are gonna\Nkeep me busy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have a long list of things\NI've been dying to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Touch nose with tongue."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Play bongos on my belly."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"Smell my dirty feet."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That didn't take nearly\Nas long as I thought it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Season 3 | Episode 9\NSpike at Your Service
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed by GrayJeager\NFr.Jeager@gmail.com
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://www.youtube.com/user/GhxBronie\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.fr (french)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do?\NWhat to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A hot air balloon ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!\NRunaway balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't know better,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I would swear that I was in the middle\Nof the dark and scary Everfree forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because this forest is full\Nof wild, dangerous animals
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean\Nthat you're gonna see one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get me,\Nyou big goons!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm running!\NI'm running!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Applejack.\NThat was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you rocketed those boulders\Nat them like they were rockets!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You... saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, don't mention it, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, we should be heading\Non back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, am I lucky you were out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, why were you out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Saw the balloon floating by\Nwith no pony in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Came out here to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you did too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was investigating\Nthe runaway hot air balloon too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,now that the mystery's been solved,\Nlet's get out here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for walking me home, Spike.\NThat was mighty kind of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I have some chores that\Nneed tending to, so see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What chores?\NI'll do them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sweet,\Nbut you don't have--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the least I can do.\NYou saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to repay the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot, Spike, that's what\Nfriends do for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need\Nto repay the favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugar, it's okay.\NIt's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, you don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something\Nthat I really need to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I hate to get in the way of you\Ndoing something you need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!\NWhat should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Apple Bloom's over yonder,\Ngiving little Piggington a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was gonna lend her a hoof, but,\Nmaybe you could lend her one instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,On the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack said I could help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!\NI could use all the help I can get!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait till Applejack sees\Nhow you sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack,\Nis it okay if I get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna be late\Nfor my Crusaders meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting fitted\Nfor water skis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You definitely don't want\Nto be late for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Water-skiing Cutie Mark,\Nhere I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, you can head on out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I reckon you have re-paid me in full\Nso we are officially even-Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't even close\Nto being even-Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Applejack, you must\Nallow me to assist you further!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't feel right to have you\Ndoing things for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please.\N- Really, you don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Pretty please.\N- It's just not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty, pretty, pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can help Granny Smith\Nand me bake some...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pies! Pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm helping Applejack\Nmake some pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, little feller,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,could you get us\Nsome more eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, oops.\NSorry, Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get something\Nto clean that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciate all your help today,\Nsugar cube, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my honor and my duty.\NToday is just the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's that now?\N- You saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the\N"Spike the Dragon Code,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you a life debt\Nand must serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what about Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't she need your help\Nand such?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I better break the news\Nto Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope she doesn't\Ntake it too hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your personal moral, ethical\NDragon Code we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you and Twilight\Nwon't be friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't be the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But it has to be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, Applejack\Njust saved my life
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,from horrible,\Ndragon-eating Timberwolves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And, as you are aware,\NI adhere to my Dragon Code
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and this means I must serve her\Nfor the rest of my natural-born days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... been an honor... being\Nyour faithful assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She said it was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really?\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So with Twilight's blessing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I am free to follow my code\Nand serve you until...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, until... forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, sugar cube, I completely\Nrespect your Dragon Code,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,truly I do, but I just can't cotton\Nwith you permanently serving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Applejack.\NMy Dragon Code is a part of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be true to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't let me do this,\NI won't be a noble dragon anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, I can't have you feeling like\Nyou're not a noble dragon, now can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Then from here on in,\Nyour wish is my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me take some of the pie\Nyou made to--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I helped bake it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You even look good\Nwhen you're chewing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who looks good\Nwhen they're chewing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna have some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a big lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 10 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Breakfast.\NA big breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you could take her plate\Nback to the kitchen and wash it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I saved Spike from some Timberwolves\Nin the Everfree Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and now he thinks\Nhe has to serve me forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What I wouldn't give to have\Nsome pony forever in my debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd get them to organize my closets,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and give me pedicures\Nand help me with my sewing--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Having somepony to do things\Nfor you would be a dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't feel right having Spike\Nthinking he owes me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And you tasted that pie.\NSometimes his help isn't that helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a broom I could borrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A.J., Rarity!\NWhat's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack saved Spike's life\Nand now he has to serve her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you having him do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wash your laundry?\NClean your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Help you with\Nyour unfinished novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine's about this awesome Pegasus
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,who's the best flyer ever and becomes\Nthe captain of the Wonderbolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:11:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How ever did you come up with that\Ningeniously woven, intricate plot line?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thing is I don't really want him\Nto serve me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know how\Nto get him to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make him help you with\Nsomething really, really hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want him to get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll quit way before there's\Neven a chance of getting hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Spike,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack was gonna\Nhelp me stack some hay
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so I could practice smashing\Nthrough it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm feeling extra,\Nextra powerful today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- You are?\N- Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of hay,\NI'm gonna smash through rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rocks?\N- Yeah, a huge tower of rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're gonna build it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- I am?\N- Yeah, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you don't want\Nto help Applejack...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I do!\NIt is Spike's Dragon Code!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me.\NThis is gonna work like a charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure he'd give up\Nafter like three rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness.\NIf it'd been me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have just pretended I didn't\Nhave anything for him to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this high enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's plenty high.\NCome on down, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad news: he actually ended up\Nbuilding the whole rock tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good news:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a rock tower\Nto knock down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna do it again,\NRainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack can re-build it for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I say "Applejack",\NI of course mean me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't think Rainbow Dash\Nneeds any more of your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My help.\NShe doesn't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NI guess I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- For now.\N- And so am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't think of one more\Nthing I need help with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have\Nto do anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you can't think\Nof anything else I can help with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly that.\NThere's nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't help you,\Nhow will I know I'm a noble dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, huh--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's things\Nyou need help with
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that you don't even realize\Nyou need help with!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If she needed help,\NI think she'd realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Applejack needs help\Nrealizing what she needs help with!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, maybe your back itches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That does feel good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Or... you might need help\Nremembering your favorite song!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dragon is\Nthe finest creature ever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's more to him\Nthan just guarding treasure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think\Nthat's her favorite--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Or... you might\Nneed help breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathing?\NI certainly do not--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See? There are plenty of things\NI can help you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't even have\Nto trouble yourself with thinking of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'll think of them!\NLet me think of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight?\NTwilight are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.\NI didn't mean to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to take a break anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Spike told you that\Nhe was gonna follow his Dragon Code
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and serve me forever for saving\Nhim from the Timberwolves,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you were okay\Nwith it, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he told you\Nall about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing maybe you were\Na little distracted when he told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Should've realized you wouldn't\Nhave let him go so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now that you know\Nwhat's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe you could talk\Nsome sense into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Applejack, I wish I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is the Dragon Code\Nwe're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you know how important\Nthe Dragon Code is to a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure am starting to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one other way Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is gonna fulfill the debt\Nhe feels he owes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,71, 72, 73, 74, 75...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, y'all,\Nhere's the deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike needs to save my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want us to shoot you out\Nof a cannon toward a hornet's nest,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and give Spike a butterfly net\Nso he can catch you mere seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,before you hit the nest and are stung\Nby a thousand angry hornets!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wear this moustache.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am gonna be attacked\Nby a Timberwolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I still wear\Nthe moustache?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When I give the signal,\NPinky Pie and Rarity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,will come running out of the woods,\Nbeing pursued by the Timberwolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start to run too,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but then pretend to get\Nmy hoof stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask Spike\Nto help me dislodge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And he will and I'll be able to get away\Nfrom the terrifying Timberwolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Having saved me\Nfrom certain doom,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike will then\Nconsider us even!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all ready\Nto play our parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but are you sure you're ready\Nto play yours, Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us your best\Ndamsel in distress move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely horrendous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this needs\Nsome serious work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, first you must lift your foreleg up\Nto your forehead like so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Applejack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No time.\NHere he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, over here, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you had something else\Nyou needed me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yes, I was just hoping\Nyou could maybe, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,sweep up all those leaves\Nfor a compost pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there are exactly 24,567,837\Nblades of grass at Sweet Apple Acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you counted\Nevery single one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a noble dragon and follower\Nof my Dragon Code, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was very convincing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Timberwolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We are doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I seem to have got\Nmy hoof caught in between two rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a damsel in distress!\NHelp me, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.\NDon't wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me from\Nthe terrifying Timberwolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he would be terrifying\Nif he wasn't... a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the clomping\Nof his claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The roar was spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And the detail on his face\Nis pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But you forgot one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,His breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can smell a real Timberwolf's\Nbreath from a mile--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late!\NI'm already on--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Timberwolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Timberwolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.\NI'm really stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No more messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it, Spike.\NYou gotta get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you just forget\Nyour Dragon Code already and go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you\Nguys back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought you were right behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My hoof was stuck and that Timberwolf\Nwas coming right at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you were actually stuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But Spike picked up a pebble,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and rocketed that thing right\Nat the huge Timberwolf's mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was something all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,'Course I wouldn't have needed help\Nif I hadn't been trying to stage a fake
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Timberwolf attack\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NWhat was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this code thing's\Nimportant to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but if something like this\Ncomes up in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,think maybe we can\Ngo back to my code,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,say that's what friends do,\Nand leave it at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I won't think\Nof you as any less noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:20:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe let's just try\Nto avoid situations where one of us
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,actually needs help the other one\Nto save their life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You got yourself a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks, Spike.\N- Happy to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know what I'd do\Nwithout you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really, really, really\Nhappy to help you!
